---
---

<section id="about" class="relative overflow-hidden px-5 py-28 md:px-10 md:py-44">
  <!-- decorative parallax layer -->
  <div aria-hidden="true">
    <span
      data-parallax="-70"
      class="text-outline-faint font-display absolute -top-6 right-[6%] text-[11rem] leading-none font-bold select-none md:text-[17rem]"
    >
      +
    </span>
    <span data-parallax="50" class="absolute right-[12%] bottom-8 hidden md:block">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 200 200" class="spin-slow h-36 w-36 lg:h-44 lg:w-44">
        <defs>
          <path id="about-circle" d="M100,100 m-78,0 a78,78 0 1,1 156,0 a78,78 0 1,1 -156,0"></path>
        </defs>
        <text fill="#8a8a86" font-size="14.5" letter-spacing="3.5" class="font-mono uppercase">
          <textPath href="#about-circle">design — test — secure — repeat —&nbsp;</textPath>
        </text>
        <text x="100" y="110" text-anchor="middle" fill="#5eead4" font-size="30">+</text>
      </svg>
    </span>
  </div>

  <div class="relative grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-12">
    <div class="md:col-span-3">
      <h2 class="font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.18em] text-muted uppercase">
        <span class="text-accent">(01)</span> About
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="md:col-span-9">
      <p data-reveal class="font-display max-w-4xl text-3xl leading-[1.12] font-medium tracking-tight text-balance md:text-5xl">
        I design software, drive the build with <span class="text-accent">AI</span>, then do my best
        to <span class="text-outline">break it</span> — before anyone else can.
      </p>

      <p data-reveal class="mt-10 max-w-2xl text-base leading-relaxed text-muted md:text-lg">
        The workflow is deliberate: I design the system, implement
        with <span class="text-ink">Claude Code</span> to strengthen my software design, development and Git skills, then
        attack the result with <span class="text-ink">black-box testing</span> — the same adversarial mindset security
        work demands.
      </p>

      <p data-fade class="mt-8 font-mono text-xs tracking-[0.14em] text-muted uppercase">
        (Off the clock: photography, road cycling, travel)
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
